arabic.title: Sa-'alt Nafsi Kteer - (سألت نفسي كتير)
text: ولا أنا جوايا و مش داري
و خمسميت حاجه و مالهمش دعوة ببعض
أنا مين و فين أنا أيه

english.title: I Asked Myself a lot
text: or am I full of evil?
Am I full of flaws or am I
Am I full of flaws or am I
Or do I have inside, without knowing,
and another five hundred unrelated things
Who am I? Where am I? What am I?
Is my way furnished with flowers?
or am I in this age

arabic.title: أنا حد تاني
text: انا عايز اعرف كل ده بيحصلّي ليه!
كتر الوجع خلاني مش قادر أكمّل
دانا لو جبل واقف مكاني مكانش اتحمّل!
مكسور وسوء الاختيار بقى خصلة فيّا
بتعب على نفسي عشان متعبش اكتر مانا تعبان
عمّال بقاوح يمكن ألقى بداية ليّا
انا حد تاني مش أنا، انا شخص تايه معرفوش
مبقتش عارف مين انا، جوايا خوف مفهمتهوش
حاسس حياتي اتلخبطت، وبتنتهي قدّام عينيّا
شايف همومي اتكوّمت، وكل يوم بتهدّ فيّا
وكأنّ حاجة مكتفاني بتشدني علشان مقومشي
وسحابة سودة مغمّياني في سكتي ومش عايزة تمشي
م الجاي خايف، مبقتش عارف ايه اللي لازم ارميه ورايا
أيّام وساكت وحقيقتي تاهت ولا حل نافع أبداً معايا
رافض أشوف نفسي ضعيف، مانا لو رضيت، احساس مخيف!
باين عليّا في الدنيا ديّا هفضل في توهة لحد النهاية
انا حد تاني مش أنا، انا شخص تايه معرفوش
مبقتش عارف مين انا، جوايا خوف مفهمتهوش

english.title: I'm someone else
text: I just want to know why all this is happening to me!
Too much pain has left me unable to keep going
Everything isn't going as it should and then what?
If I were a mountain, I still wouldn't be able to take it
I'm broken and making bad choices has become a habit
And I've tried to change my life a bit
I work hard on myself so that I won't get any more pain than I already have
I keep lying to myself; maybe I'll find me a new beginning
I'm someone else, I'm not who I am, I'm someone lost that I don't know
I don't know who I am anymore, I have a fear inside me that I cannot understand
I feel like my life is a mess, and it's running out before my eyes
I have burdens piling up, and they're breaking me everyday
It's like something it holding me from getting up
And there's a dark cloud that's standing in my way, making it hard for me to see
I'm afraid of what's to come, I no longer know what should I put behind me
Days pass in silence, reality is lost and no solution is working at all
I refuse to see myself this weak; if I accept it, it's a terrifying feeling
It seems like I'm going to be lost in this life until the end
I'm someone else, I'm not who I am, I'm someone lost that I don't know
I don't know who I am anymore, I have a fear inside me that I cannot understand

arabic.title: ليه جيت عليّا
text: و ههدى انا فى خلال يومين
لا انسى ان انا اجيب سيرتك تانى
و ههدى انا فى خلال يومين

english.title: Why did you come this time?
text: Look at me while you are talking
I want to learn how to be an administrator
Can calm down and turn off the fire
If you think I will leave you
If this is wrong with you
I was wrong inside your life
You are a teacher in my collapse
Why did you come this time?
And I came to love the years
I thought it was wrong for this time
There is no rest for you, nostalgia
And do not think that I am normal
And guide me in two days
Who did you do with me?
Let me see your heart burn
I see you do not feel
I am the exit from your life
And it will be a problem and transgression
And I am talking about words only
Do not forget that I answer your resume again
You got out of my account
Why did you come this time?
And I came to love the years
I thought it was wrong for this time
There is no rest for you, nostalgia
And do not think that I am normal
And guide me in two days

arabic.title: ملكش مكان
text: دورى إنى أوجع ما انت واجعنى زمان
اللي فات كله مات يلا شكراً سلام
اللي فات كله مات يلا شكراً سلام
كنت جنبك حاربت وتعبت ومشاعرك رخاص
فجأة بسهولة سيبت وراجعلي لا ابعد خلاص
اللي فات كله مات يلا شكراً سلام
ايوة انا هو اللي قويت عليه
شوفت القوة عملت فيا أنا ايه
اللي فات كله مات يلا شكراً سلام

english.title: There is no place for you
text: You want to come back, forget it, there is no place for you
It's my turn to hurt, you already hurt me a long time ago
No matter what you say to me, there won't be another chance
You're coming back to me when you found me living
What's gone is gone, thank you and goodbye
I'm done and I forgot, no words will help
What's gone is gone, thank you and goodbye
I'm done and I forgot, no words will help
I was next to you, I fought and got tired, your feelings are cheap
Suddenly and easily, you left and you're coming back to me, never, it's over
What's gone is gone, thank you and goodbye
I'm done and I forgot, no words will help
Yes, I am the one who you became strong on him
See what strength did to me?
Forget your coming back and walk quietly
And know my value when you see me waking up
What's gone is gone, thank you and goodbye
I'm done and I forgot, no words will help

arabic.title: اهو ده اللى صار
text: و خير بلادنا مهوش في ايدنا
و بدال ما يشمت فينا حاسد
و بدال ما يشمت فينا حاسد

english.title: This is What Happened
text: And so this is what happened
and this is how it was
You have no right to blame me
How can you blame me, oh our master
when the riches of our country are not even in our hands?
How can you blame me, oh our master
when the riches of our country are not even in our hands?
Speak of things that would benefit us
and then come back to blaming me
And so this is what happened
and this is how it was
You have no right to blame me
Take good care of [your] beloved ones
They are the supports of the cause
And so this is what happened
and this is how it was
You have no right to blame me
And instead of allowing an envious hater to be happy at our expense,
and get up and let's fight
And instead of allowing an envious hater to be happy at our expense,
and get up and let's fight
then we would all become one hand
And the hands would become strong
And so this is what happened
and this is how it was
You have no right to blame me
And so this is what happened
and this is how it was; You have no right
You have no right to blame me
